a Bears]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Craig |first1=Mitchell |title=Ballina Bears take out LJ Hooker League cricket premiership |url=https://www.northernstar.com.au/news/ballina-bears-take-out-lj-hooker-league-cricket-pr/2207114/#/0/ |website=[[The Northern Star]] |accessdate=25 March 2019 |language=en |date=24 March 2014}}</ref>\n*2014/15: Cudgen<ref>{{cite web |last1=Craig |first1=Mitchell |title=Cudgen the benchmark in FNC cricket after going back-to-back |url=https://www.northernstar.com.au/news/cudgen-the-benchmark-in-fnc-cricket-after-going-ba/2970348/ |website=[[The Northern Star]] |accessdate=25 March 2019 |language=en |date=21 March 2016}}</ref>\n*2015/16: Cudgen<ref>{{cite web |last1=Craig |first1=Mitchell |title=Cudgen the benchmark in FNC cricket after going back-to-back |url=https://www.northernstar.com.au/news/cudgen-the-benchmark-in-fnc-cricket-after-going-ba/2970348/ |website=[[The Northern Star]] |accessdate=25 March 2019 |language=en |date=21 March 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=McKenzie |first1=D |title=Pottsville down as Bears go on attack |url=https://www.tweeddailynews.com.au/news/pottsville-down-as-bears-go-on-attack/3130129/ |website=[[Tweed Daily News]] |accessdate=25 March 2019 |language=en |date=10 January 2017}}</ref>\n*2016/17: [[Alstonville Cricket Club|Alstonville]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Craig |first1=Mitchell |title=Season sinks for Soilers in Hooker League cricket |url=https://www.northernstar.com.au/news/season-sinks-for-soilers-in-hooker-league-cricket/3346766/ |website=[[The Northern Star]] |accessdate=25 March 2019 |language=en |date=27 February 2018}}</ref>\n*2017/18: Cudgen\n*2018/19: Cudgen\n*2019/20: Cudgen<ref>{{cite web |title=Cudgen cricketers enjoy a decade of dominance |url=https://www.tweeddailynews.com.au/news/cudgen-cricketers-enjoy-a-decade-of-dominance/3984291/ |website=[[Tweed Daily News]] |accessdate=2 April 2020 |language=en |date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Player of the Year==\n\nThe following players have been na